{"type":"message","id":"093cfb61","parentId":"f8ce97d8","timestamp":"2026-05-26T06:16:05.922Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Clean. So where does this leave us:\n\n- **Codex CLI** — uninstalled, won't work with FreeRide\n- **aider** — uninstalled, works great with OpenRouter but we removed it\n- **OpenCode** — uninstalled, nice TUI but needs config setup\n\nThe reality is you already have a solid setup: **OpenClaw + FreeRide + sub-agents** handles coding tasks well on free OpenRouter models. If you want a dedicated terminal coding agent down the road, `aider` is the easiest to wire up to OpenRouter.\n\nWant me to look at anything else, or close out this thread?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":296,"output":140,"cacheRead":70784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71220,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779776140541,"responseId":"gen-1779776140-WSl9IyZSeDgeCFegCyi3"}}
