{"type":"message","id":"b4af859e","parentId":"cd433c6e","timestamp":"2026-05-26T18:47:04.925Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Not much — we installed it, confirmed it works with OpenRouter, then you asked to uninstall everything so I removed it.\n\nIt's a solid terminal coding agent though. If you want it back:\n\n```\npip3 install aider-chat\n```\n\nThen use it with FreeRide like:\n\n```\nAIDER_OPENROUTER_API_KEY=\"***\" aider --model openrouter/qwen/qwen3-coder:free\n```\n\nIt supports multi-file edits, git diffs, plan mode — pretty capable. Want me to reinstall it?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":50795,"output":112,"cacheRead":9984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60891,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779821214388,"responseId":"gen-1779821214-79rK1GcWlheV6yjljYLv"}}
