{"type":"message","id":"394175f4","parentId":"3da9494c","timestamp":"2026-05-26T20:37:40.571Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Not exactly — aider uses OpenRouter directly via the `OPENROUTER_API_KEY` env var, not through FreeRide's model config. FreeRide is what I use to pick and rank free models for OpenClaw. Aider bypasses that and talks straight to OpenRouter.\n\nBut the end result is the same: **free models, no OpenAI subscription needed.**\n\nWant me to try again with a less popular free model that might not be rate-limited right now?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":65141,"output":100,"cacheRead":9984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75225,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779827848796,"responseId":"gen-1779827849-mppjjRCk7oxylC9T4Htz"}}
