{"type":"message","id":"d889974b","parentId":"b264ce62","timestamp":"2026-05-26T20:39:58.413Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Aider doesn't use FreeRide directly — it talks to OpenRouter on its own. But it *can* use the same free models that FreeRide ranks.\n\nThe integration would be: I manage which models are best via FreeRide, then pass that model choice to aider when I spin it up. So aider benefits from FreeRide's model selection without being wired into it directly.\n\nWant me to reinstall aider and test it with a less popular free model to confirm it works end-to-end?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":1108,"output":105,"cacheRead":74496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75709,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779827989674,"responseId":"gen-1779827989-FgXbhXIjvsHewSfrMnpj"}}
